herdstat - http://developer.berlios.de/projects/herdstat/
See AUTHORS for developer contact information.

Features
========
herdstat is a multi-purpose query tool capable of things such as:

    * Displaying herd information (bugzilla alias, developer information,
      package information).
    * Displaying developer information (email address, real name (if present
      in herds.xml), herd information, package information).
    * Displaying category/package metadata.

Bugs
====
Please submit bugs and patches via http://bugs.gentoo.org/.

Usage
=====
Read herdstat(1) for information on using herdstat. Running herdstat --help
will also display detailed usage information.
